---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import LandingHeaderEn from "../../components/LandingHeaderEn.astro";
import FooterEn from "../../components/FooterEn.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Us | AI Agent Platform | VivaSpeak"
  description="VivaSpeak: conversational AI agent platform. Voice, web chat, WhatsApp, CRM and Salesforce integration. Multi-location and editable knowledge base."
  canonical="https://vivaspeak.com/en/about/"
  alternateEs="https://vivaspeak.com/sobre-nosotros/"
  alternateEn="https://vivaspeak.com/en/about/"
  lang="en"
>
  <LandingHeaderEn ctaLabel="Request demo" ctaHref="/en/#schedule" secondaryHref="/en/" />

  <main id="main-content">
    <section class="about-container" style="max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 24px 100px; text-align: left;">
      <h1>About VivaSpeak</h1>
      
      <p>
        VivaSpeak develops conversational AI agents for businesses that need to automate calls, web chat and digital channels 24/7. Our platform lets you configure agent behavior, prompts and knowledge base, integrating with CRMs like Salesforce, calendars and internal systems.
      </p>

      <p>
        We're not just a voice agent. VivaSpeak is a platform where each company defines how their assistant should behave: what information it can provide, how it should close appointments and what data to record. Everything is centralized in a panel with transcripts, metrics and automations.
      </p>

      <h2>Who we are</h2>
      <p>
        We work with clinics, real estate agencies and service companies in Spain and Latin America. 
        We are a team specialized in customer service automation and development of conversational AI agents for businesses that handle high call volumes.
      </p>

      <h2>Platform</h2>
      <p>
        From the VivaSpeak panel you can:
      </p>
      <ul style="margin: 0 0 1rem 1.25rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        <li>Edit the agent's knowledge base.</li>
        <li>Configure routing rules by location or promotion.</li>
        <li>Integrate Salesforce or other CRMs via API.</li>
        <li>Manage leads in a built-in lightweight CRM.</li>
        <li>Enable voice agent, web chat or both on the same knowledge.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Sectors</h2>
      <ul style="margin: 0 0 1rem 1.25rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        <li><strong>Clinics</strong> — Virtual assistant for clinics: schedules appointments, checks availability and manages reception 24/7.</li>
        <li><strong>Real estate</strong> — Multi-location intelligent switchboard, lead capture, automatic filtering by promotion and direct CRM registration.</li>
        <li><strong>HR</strong> — Call automation for recruitment: screens candidates and schedules interviews.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Integrations</h2>
      <p>
        Integration with WhatsApp Business API, Google Calendar, Microsoft Bookings, Salesforce and other CRMs via API. Compatible with WordPress and corporate sites to install web chat in minutes.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        To learn more about how an AI voice agent can help you,
        <a href="/en/#schedule">schedule a free demo</a> or email us at 
        <a href="mailto:hello@vivaspeak.com">hello@vivaspeak.com</a>. You can also call 
        <a href="tel:+34951798932">+34 951 798 932</a> — Valeria, our AI voice agent, will answer.
      </p>
      <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;">
        <a href="/en/" class="btn-primary">Back to home</a>
      </p>

      <h2>Intelligent Automation for Businesses</h2>
      <p>
        VivaSpeak combines voice agent, web chatbot and CRM integration in a single platform. Automates inbound calls, logs opportunities in Salesforce, sends promotion information and enables multi-location support scaling without expanding human teams.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
  <FooterEn />
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-container h1 { font-size: 2rem; color: var(--primary-dark); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: center; }
  .about-container h2 { font-size: 1.35rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .about-container p { line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .about-container a { color: var(--primary-dark); font-weight: 600; }
  .about-container .btn-primary { color: var(--white); }
</style>
